HEADWORD: Overleap
<hw>O`ver*leap"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>oferhle⟦aacute⟧pan</ets>. See <er>Over</er>, and
<er>Leap</er>.]</ety> <def>To leap over or across; hence, to omit; to
ignore.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Let me <xex>o'erleap</xex> that custom.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

